  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">ZLECAB II (Zaman Lebidi Cash Bridge) &#x2013; OI-ATAD</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">- Making practical arrangements at community level for how transfers will take place and be recorded and arranging security 
- Carrying out a pre-distribution capacity building and training
- Proving support to HAP and accountability processes
- Distributing the cash to beneficiary households through mobile company
- Carrying out pre/post distribution monitoring 
- Carrying out a learning workshop</narrative>
  </description>
  <description type="2">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">- Vulnerable households are able to meet their immediate food and essential non-food needs 
- Improvement of the nutritional status of children under the age of 5 years
- Vulnerable households are able to meet minimum short-term expenditure and debt service requirements  
- Support to the normal functioning of the local economy and avoidance of market collapse
- Ensuring continuity of implementation of the BRACED Zaman Lebidi project
-	Maintaining high levels or trust and respect between communities and local IPs
-	Maintained programme credibility</narrative>
  </description>
